            <title><![CDATA[【🙅🏻#胃不舒服不要乱吃药#】辣椒、洋葱、巧克力等含糖和油脂较多的食物，都容易引起胃酸增多，#胃爱泛酸这些食物要少吃# 。[话筒]医生提醒，胃部不适不要...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🙅🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%83%83%E4%B8%8D%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%B9%B1%E5%90%83%E8%8D%AF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%83%83%E4%B8%8D%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%B9%B1%E5%90%83%E8%8D%AF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#胃不舒服不要乱吃药#</span></a>】辣椒、洋葱、巧克力等含糖和油脂较多的食物，都容易引起胃酸增多，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%83%83%E7%88%B1%E6%B3%9B%E9%85%B8%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%91%E5%90%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%83%83%E7%88%B1%E6%B3%9B%E9%85%B8%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%91%E5%90%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#胃爱泛酸这些食物要少吃#</span></a> 。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒，胃部不适不要乱吃药，如果长期吃抑酸药，胃酸分泌就会减少，甚至可能导致胃部大环境发生变化。我们应该尽量通过改变生活习惯等方式，来缓解胃部不适👇🏻（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6YchJAz" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
